### ========================================
### 微信小程序登录 API 测试脚本
### 使用方式：VS Code 安装 REST Client 插件后直接运行
### ========================================

### 环境变量定义
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/v1
@testCode = 081aBcde2fGHij0w4qcd2YZKde0aBcda
@testUsername = admin
@testPassword = admin123

### ========================================
### 1. 测试微信登录接口（自动注册）
### ========================================

POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/wechat/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "{{testCode}}",
  "nickname": "测试用户",
  "avatarUrl": "https://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/test.jpg"
}

### 预期响应：
# {
#   "code": 200,
#   "message": "success",
#   "data": {
#     "token": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9...",
#     "refreshToken": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9...",
#     "user": {
#       "userId": 57,
#       "username": "wx_12345678",
#       "nickname": "测试用户",
#       "avatar": "https://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/test.jpg",
#       "role": "student",
#       "points": 100,
#       "level": 1
#     }
#   }
# }

### ========================================
### 2. 验证登录后获取用户信息
### ========================================

### 先获取 Token（从上一步响应中复制）
@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJyb2xlIjoic3R1ZGVudCIsInVzZXJJZCI6NTcsInVzZXJuYW1lIjoid3hfMTIzNDU2NzgiLCJpYXQiOjE3MzQ1MDAwMDAsImV4cCI6MTczNDUwNzIwMH0.xxx

GET {{baseUrl}}/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 预期响应：
# {
#   "code": 200,
#   "message": "success",
#   "data": {
#     "uid": 57,
#     "username": "wx_12345678",
#     "nickname": "测试用户",
#     "points": 100,
#     "level": 1
#   }
# }

### ========================================
### 3. 测试绑定已有账号
### ========================================

### 前置条件：先使用普通账号登录获取 Token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "account": "{{testUsername}}",
  "password": "{{testPassword}}"
}

###

### 使用普通账号的 Token 调用绑定接口
@normalToken = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.xxx

POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/wechat/bind-account
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{testUsername}}",
  "password": "{{testPassword}}"
}

### 预期响应：
# {
#   "code": 200,
#   "message": "账号绑定成功"
# }

### ========================================
### 4. 测试错误场景
### ========================================

### 场景 1：无效的 code
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/wechat/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "invalid_code_12345"
}

### 预期响应：
# {
#   "code": 400,
#   "message": "微信登录凭证（code）无效"
# }

###

### 场景 2：code 为空
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/wechat/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": ""
}

### 预期响应：
# {
#   "code": 400,
#   "message": "微信登录 code 不能为空"
# }

###

### 场景 3：绑定账号时密码错误
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/wechat/bind-account
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{testUsername}}",
  "password": "wrong_password"
}

### 预期响应：
# {
#   "code": 400,
#   "message": "密码错误"
# }

### ========================================
### 5. 数据库验证查询
### ========================================

### 在 MySQL 中执行以下查询验证结果：

-- 查看最新注册的微信用户
-- SELECT u_id, username, nickname, wechat_openid, points, level, created_at
-- FROM user
-- WHERE wechat_openid IS NOT NULL
-- ORDER BY u_id DESC
-- LIMIT 5;

-- 查看积分日志
-- SELECT user_id, points, type, description, created_at
-- FROM points_log
-- WHERE user_id = (SELECT u_id FROM user WHERE wechat_openid IS NOT NULL ORDER BY u_id DESC LIMIT 1)
-- ORDER BY created_at DESC;

-- 查看绑定了微信的账号
-- SELECT u_id, username, nickname, wechat_openid, wechat_unionid
-- FROM user
-- WHERE username = 'admin' AND wechat_openid IS NOT NULL;

### ========================================
### 测试注意事项
### ========================================

# 1. 测试前确保后端服务已启动：mvn spring-boot:run
# 2. 确保数据库迁移已执行（添加 wechat_openid 字段）
# 3. 确保 application.yml 中配置了微信 AppID 和 AppSecret
# 4. 真实测试需要使用微信开发者工具获取真实 code
# 5. 每个 code 只能使用一次，测试时注意更换 code
# 6. Token 有效期 2 小时，过期后需要重新登录

### ========================================
### 常见错误码说明
### ========================================

# 40029: code 无效或已过期
# 45011: 接口调用频率限制（每分钟 100 次）
# 40163: code 已被使用
# -1: 微信系统繁忙

### ========================================
### 调试技巧
### ========================================

# 1. 查看后端日志：backend/logs/spring.log
# 2. 查看控制台输出：微信登录相关日志都有 [微信登录] 前缀
# 3. 使用 Postman 或 Apifox 导入此文件进行测试
# 4. 微信开发者工具 → Console → 查看 uni.login() 返回的 code
